channel.title: Vicetone - Way Back (Ft. Cozi Zuehlsdorff) Remix Competition
channel.description:
So for any non-auxy users (I suppose it could actually work with Auxy too), Monstercat is hosting a Remix competition on Splice for [Vicetone's Way Back w/ Cozi Zuehlsdorff.](https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZaRYaTT2Xcs)
Competition goes till May, 28th And you have to sigh up before hand (it's free, u just need to make a splice acc to DL the stems)
Go solo at it, or maybe grab someone else for a collab, but i just wanted to share the competition around here for the opportunity if anyone wants to take a shot at it.
https://splice.com/VicetoneOfficial/Wayback?utm_source=vicetone&utm_medium=artist&utm_term=wayback-remix
![16%20AM|689x252](upload://9TdFzl2YHzHK4US02fefWUD98El.jpg)
(There are more details/ rules n stuff on the actual page)
